{"tid":240391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林寶自焚　鄰車響按提司機","createTime":"2017-05-12T11:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T19:49:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1c494cdd8dc4af79b327093dc76178fb625ae3","tid":240391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20018813&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20018813%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170512&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f5efd88a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20018813%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170512&h=f9c12cb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20018813&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170512</a><br />\n<br />\n林寶自焚　鄰車響按提司機<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n林寶堅尼後座起火，現場濃煙直冒。讀者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一輛價值逾200萬元的林寶堅尼超跑，昨在觀塘道行駛期間，車後座突然起火焚燒，火勢猛烈，司機及時跳車逃生，消防接報到場迅速將火救熄，司機並無受傷，初步調查疑電線短路起火，並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n疑電線短路<br />\n<br />\n肇事白色林寶堅尼跑車，型號為GALLARDO COUPE，2004年首次登記，當時值260萬元，登記車主為38歲高盛亞洲投資管理團隊主管鄧智傑。<br />\n昨午2時許，鄧駕駛林寶堅尼跑車，沿觀塘道往旺角方向行駛，突有其他司機向他響按，指其座駕後座位置起火冒煙。鄧遂將車停在路旁報警求助，現場濃煙直冒，途人掩鼻離去，消防出動一喉一煙帽隊，約8分鐘將火救熄，跑車車尾嚴重焚毀，消防初步調查，疑電線短路致火警，鄧在場協助調查。<br />\n■記者梁澤岡<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n消防到場將火救熄。"},{"pid":"626f63cbaf49b212551a53200ae42d07cddba0b9","tid":240391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170512/large/12la8p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170512%2Flarge%2F12la8p01.jpg&h=f5570fce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74f9f0f736840981871ee67882dccb2b43c8c2ac","tid":240391,"uid":8497,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:33:35.000Z","msg":"應該將會有一班現實乜都無既人笑鳩佢抵死"},{"pid":"8d995a51b764d03ef6c084b5836acc4e21689825","tid":240391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170512/large/12la8p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170512%2Flarge%2F12la8p06.jpg&h=ff9206d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f05bf12d2422a2b6b249f05b826b368caca81390","tid":240391,"uid":56203,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"睇錯林鄭自焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818b9372fae4a6a95d64212209ea3420fccf1eec","tid":240391,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯林鄭自焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入黎前拍曬手掌"},{"pid":"68d202576a0cb183efc03c1020d7b76ddb711f9c","tid":240391,"uid":5713,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇錯林鄭自焚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入黎前拍曬手掌</blockquote><br />\n你兩個要驗眼"},{"pid":"917e6db1416ba2c1da10111fbb234a9f7d79ac5b","tid":240391,"uid":57962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:45:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"462276ca3539c3e92b853288f1c9d45563172521","tid":240391,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12